snippet.title: Polymega Gameplays - Army Men 3D [PlayStation - PAL]
snippet.description:
The Army Men jump into PS action in a fully 3D environment, allowing you to use all the weapons found in the original, but from a 3rd person perspective. You can also blast away with a mate in a multiplayer mode or two.

Army Men (C) Take Two Interactive
Developed by The 3DO Company
BIOS Used: Polymega BIOS
